<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Admiral,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">To born in this world</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">It is a miracle, for I am the same as you, or am I?</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">You are determined, fierce and strong.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">And I am the one who serves</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">For you are the one I love the most.  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Admiral,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Even when there are others around,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I do not mind, for you are happy, I am happy too.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I decide it is fine, to go on sortie, to go on expedition</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">For you are the one I love the most.  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Admiral,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I remember there were times,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">That I am heavily damaged</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">You say “hang in there”</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I am not scare you see, because I believe in your decision</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">For you are the one I love the most.  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Admiral,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Why today the sky seems dark</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">You send me to a place so hot, I feel uncomfortable</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I am not a human, unlike you</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I guess we are different after all</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">But I still care</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">For you are the one I love the most.  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Dear Admiral,</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">The heat is overwhelming</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">My body is disappearing into thin air</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I wish I could go on one last sortie with you, if that is not too much to ask.</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">I can hear the shattering sound</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">But Admiral, I am smiling, so don’t be sad</p>

<p class="MsoNormal">For you are the one I love the most.  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">  </p>

<p class="MsoNormal">Thank you… and goodbye.</p>
